## Daily Workflow

### Starting a new bead

```bash
# Check what's ready to work on
bd ready --json

# Start working on a bead
bd update spanish-academic-44 --status in_progress
```

### While working

- Follow the architecture principles in [CLAUDE.md](CLAUDE.md)
- Use the base templates created in Phase 2
- Run relevant scripts from Phase 3 to validate your work

### Completing a bead

```bash
# Mark as completed
bd close spanish-academic-44 --reason "Documentation complete, principles defined"

# Run validation
npm run validate-all  # (after scripts are built)
```

